      "fact_id": "F3",
      "why_it_matters": "Confirms the specific version requirement (0.80.0) associated with the amendment, validating the mitigation path mentioned in F1."
    }
  ],
  "decision_summary": "The SortedDirectories amendment provides a necessary bug fix and structural improvement to the ledger. While it poses a risk to unupgraded nodes, this is a standard breaking change managed by version upgrades. The benefit of fixing undeleted directory pages outweighs the manageable risk of upgrading to version 0.80.0.",
